Wildrider walks out of the base, following behind Astrotrain. "Yeah, 
yeah, lets get going," He says in a loud annoying voice. 

Motormaster frowns. "If I wantedt to put it away where if belong, it 
would be down your throat." he spits out suerly. He grabs his sword 
with one arm, clenches it in his fist, then reefs it out, sending the 
little Decepticon flying. "Fine then, repair the machine."
